import React from 'react'
import * as rb from 'react-bootstrap'
import {ReactComponent as Logo} from '../Imgs/upload.svg'

class TopNavBar extends React.Component{

    render(){

        return (
            
            <rb.Navbar bg="white">
                <rb.Navbar.Brand style={{fontSize:30}}>
                    Filter:
                </rb.Navbar.Brand>
                <rb.Navbar.Toggle />
                <rb.Nav>
                    <rb.NavDropdown>
                        <rb.NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.1">Action</rb.NavDropdown.Item>
                        <rb.NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.2">Another action</rb.NavDropdown.Item>
                        <rb.NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.3">Something else here</rb.NavDropdown.Item>
                        <rb.NavDropdown.Divider />
                        <rb.NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.4">Separated link</rb.NavDropdown.Item>
                    </rb.NavDropdown>
                </rb.Nav>
                <rb.Navbar.Collapse className="justify-content-end">
                    <rb.Button className="text-right" id="importCases" style={{textSize:15}}>
                        <Logo style={{width:30, height:30, paddingRight:7.4}} id="uploadLogo"/>
                        IMPORT SUSPECTED CASES
                    </rb.Button>
                </rb.Navbar.Collapse>
            </rb.Navbar>
        )

    }

}

export default TopNavBar
